<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bibliography | PolitiCore</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        :root { --bg-dark: #0a0a0c; --accent: #10b981; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg-dark); color: #e4e4e7; }
        .source-card { background: #111; border: 1px solid #222; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; margin-top: 2rem; }
        .source-header { padding: 15px 20px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; }
        .source-header h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .fact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1px; background: #222; }
        .fact-card { background: #111; padding: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #aaa; }
        .fact-card strong { color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 1rem; }
        .bib-card { border-left: 4px solid #27272a; padding: 1rem; background: #16161a; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen pb-20">
    <header class="border-b border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="font-black tracking-tighter text-xl uppercase">POLITI<span class="text-emerald-500">CORE</span></span>
            <nav class="flex gap-4">
                <a href="glossary.html" class="px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-zinc-800 text-xs font-bold text-zinc-400">Glossary</a>
                <a href="bibliography.html" class="px-4 py-2 rounded bg-emerald-600/10 border border-emerald-600/30 text-xs font-bold text-emerald-400">Bibliography</a>
                <a href="fact-generator.html" class="px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-zinc-800 text-xs font-bold text-zinc-400">Generator</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mt-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 font-mono text-emerald-500 uppercase">Academic Bibliography</h1>
        
        <div class="source-card">
            <div class="source-header" style="background:#333">
                <h2>Digital Research Archives</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="fact-grid">
                <div class="fact-card"><strong>Marxists Internet Archive (MIA)</strong>Primary documents for early revolutionary theory.</div>
                <div class="fact-card"><strong>The Anarchist Library</strong>Database for decentralized and anti-state social theory.</div>
                <div class="fact-card"><strong>Library of Congress</strong>Declassified Soviet 'Revelations from the Russian Archives'.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Core Literature</h2>
            <div class="bib-card">
                <p class="text-white font-semibold">Murray Rothbard</p>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 italic">For a New Liberty (1973)</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
